===评论===
对这部影片的评论普遍具有负面性；烂番茄网站把这部影片列为100部最差影片的第22位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/disaster_movie/ |title=Disaster Movie Movie Reviews, Pictures - Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2008-09-05 |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |archive-date=2011-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501223535/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/disaster_movie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Metacritic给这部电影的打分是15%，基于12评论<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/disastermovie |title=Disaster Movie (2008): Reviews |accessdate=2008-09-05 |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |archive-date=2010-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704202441/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/disastermovie |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它被列入Empire的50部最坏的电影<ref name="The 50 Worst Movies Ever">{{cite web | url = http://www.empireonline.com/features/50-worst-movies-ever/default.asp?film=14 | title = The 50 Worst Movies Ever | work = [[Empire_(film_magazine)|Empire]] | accessdate = 2013-06-03 | archive-date = 2015-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151018024531/http://www.empireonline.com/features/50-worst-movies-ever/default.asp?film=14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，电影有史以来66部最差的电影<ref name=TotalFilm>{{cite web|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/66-worst-movies-of-all-time|title=66 Worst Movies Of All Time|date=2012-02-15|work=[[Total_Film|Total Film]]|accessdate=2013-09-30|archive-date=2014-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726052200/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/66-worst-movies-of-all-time|dead-url=no}}</ref>和MRQE的 50部最糟糕的电影(它拥有17分,得分最低的在网站上) <ref name="MRQE50">{{cite web |title=50 Worst Movies |work=[[Movie_Review_Query_Engine|Movie Review Query Engine]] |url=http://www.mrqe.com/movies/special/50_worst_movies |accessdate=2011-03-07 |archive-date=2010-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100106000455/http://www.mrqe.com/movies/special/50_worst_movies |dead-url=no }}</ref>。灾难大电影首映后几天就成为了IMDb 100部评价最低的电影中的最低一部<ref name="Byrnes">{{cite news|last=Byrnes|first=Paul|title=Disaster Movie|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/entertainment/film/film-reviews/disaster-movie/2008/10/02/1222651235778.html|work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|accessdate=June 3, 2013|date=October 2, 2008|archive-date=2018-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227160013/https://www.smh.com.au/news/entertainment/film/film-reviews/disaster-movie/2008/10/02/1222651235778.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Solomons|first=Jason|title=Disaster Movie|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2008/sep/07/comedy|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|accessdate=June 3, 2013|date=September 6, 2008|archive-date=2008-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913124807/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2008/sep/07/comedy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

卫报的詹森·所罗门写到“没有什么可以传达灾难电影的严峻性，这部电影将成为有史以来最糟糕的一部电影。”沃特敦每日时报的亚当托拜认为，“我只是不明白为什么有人竟然还感觉不到《灾难大电影》是有史以来最糟糕的一部电影”，他进一步补充说，电影的标题非常恰当，因为电影本身就是“一个灾难”<ref>{{cite news|last=Tobias|first=Adam|title=Disaster Movie one of the worst films of all time|url=http://www.wdtimes.com/features/screen_scenes/article_a665de71-6454-5ce5-9454-d13b9ad9ee18.html|work=[[Watertown_Daily_Times|Watertown Daily Times]]|accessdate=June 3, 2013|date=September 5, 2008|archive-date=2017-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709045703/http://www.wdtimes.com/features/screen_scenes/article_a665de71-6454-5ce5-9454-d13b9ad9ee18.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《泰晤士报》评论这部电影是2008年最糟糕的电影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article5245052.ece?token=null&offset=84&page=8 |title=The 100 Worst Movies of 2008 |accessdate=2009-12-12|publisher=The Times | location=London | date=2008-12-08 |first1=Anushka |last1=Asthana|author-link1=Anushka Asthana}}</ref>。

发布在烂番茄网站上面唯一积极的评论来自墨尔本时代报的吉姆·斯肯布里。斯肯布里称这部电影是“愚蠢的，但是同时也不可否认是有趣的，在很多方面都可以体现出来”，这部电影被授予5颗星星中的3颗<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/entertainment/film/film-reviews/disaster-movie/2008/10/09/1223145526498.html|title=Disaster Movie Review|work=The Age|accessdate=October 9, 2008|location=Melbourne|first1=Jim|last1=Schembri|archive-date=2017-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128080146/http://www.theage.com.au/news/entertainment/film/film-reviews/disaster-movie/2008/10/09/1223145526498.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
最积极的主要评论者，列在Metacritic或者烂番茄网站上面的是娱乐周报的欧文·葛雷博曼，他给了这部影片一个C+的分数并且评论到：“这部电影残忍地表达了朱诺的自鸣得意，她说着一些官话，而且非常有趣的是汉娜·蒙塔娜临死之前还在搞什么促销产品活动”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20222674,00.html |title=Movie Review |accessdate=2008-09-03 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205190501/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20222674,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>葛雷博曼之前也发布过一次积极的评论。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/epic_movie/ |title=Epic Movie Movie Reviews, Pictures - Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2008-08-30 |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |archive-date=2021-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404123524/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/epic_movie |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/epic-movie |title=Epic Movie (2007): Reviews |accessdate=2008-08-30 |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}</ref>

===票房绩效===
国内首次公演，《灾难大电影》首映获得的票房收入是$2,023,130，三个周末的收入是$5,836,973，四个周末的收入是$6,945,535（包括劳动节）。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=disastermovie.htm| title=Daily Box Office Grosses for ''Disaster Movie'' (2008)| publisher=Box Office Mojo| accessdate=2008-09-01| archive-date=2008-12-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205194649/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=disastermovie.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>周末的排名是第7名。达拉斯晨报预测电影周末的收入要跌落1700万美元。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dallasnews.com/sharedcontent/dws/ent/stories/DN-boxofficebuzz_0829gl.ART.State.Edition1.4d574d9.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-10-15 |archive-date=2008-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205234153/http://www.dallasnews.com/sharedcontent/dws/ent/stories/DN-boxofficebuzz_0829gl.ART.State.Edition1.4d574d9.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>影片没有之前发布的那么成功。在一项2000万美元的预算上，国内总收入为$14,190,901，海外票房为$17,492,474，全球总票房为$31,683,375，<ref name="bom"/>少于《[[这不是斯巴达|这不是斯巴达]]》总收入的一半。

==家庭媒体==
DVD和蓝光光碟发布于2009年1月6日。它们都包含一个未分级的“灾难性的”版本和一个剧场版本，两个都有相同的附加设备。大约有410934张DVD被出售了，带来了8447690美元的收入（2009年10月更新）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2008/DISAT-DVD.php |title=Disaster Movie - DVD Sales |publisher=The Numbers |date= |accessdate=2011-05-07 |archive-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402070037/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2008/DISAT-DVD.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

